title.rendered: Wrangler NFR Round 2 LIVE Las Vegas Rodeo 12/9/2023

content.rendered:
Get ready for another thrilling night of rodeo action as the 2023 Wrangler National Finals Rodeo (NFR) presented by Teton Ridge continues with Round 2 on Saturday, December 9th, 2023. The competition heats up at the Thomas & Mack Center in Las Vegas, Nevada, with cowboys and cowgirls battling it out for the coveted NFR championship titles.

Here’s what you need to know about WRANGLER NFR Round 2:

Date: Saturday, December 9, 2023
Time: 8:45 PM ET
Location: Thomas & Mack Center, Las Vegas, Nevada
Round: Round 2
Events: Bareback Riding, Steer Wrestling, Team Roping, Saddle Bronc Riding, Tie-Down Roping, Barrel Racing, Bull Riding

Stream the Wrangler NFR Round 2 LIVE from Las Vegas: Start your free trial today!
